    <!-- Application Structure Plan: A single-page, thematic dashboard structure. We will not mirror the report's linear sections. Instead, we'll use a persuasive narrative flow: Hero (Value Prop), The Problem (Market Gap), The Solution (Process Flow), Revenue Model (Interactive Chart), and Results (KPIs & Pipeline). This structure guides the user through the "why, how, what" of the business in a more engaging, data-driven way, prioritizing visual digestion over text. Navigation is handled by a sticky header with smooth-scrolling JS. -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices:
        1. Market Gap (Problem): Report Info (-86% VC vs +72% Public) -> Goal: Show the opportunity -> Viz: Bar Chart (Chart.js) -> Interaction: Hover tooltips -> Justification: Stark visual comparison of opposing trends.
        2. Service Journey (Solution): Report Info (4-step process) -> Goal: Explain the core service flow -> Viz: HTML/Tailwind horizontal flexbox diagram -> Interaction: Clickable (future-proof) -> Justification: Visually intuitive process flow, avoids text walls. NO SVG/Mermaid. (Removed private investment step).
        3. Success Fee (Revenue): Report Info (Gradual 3-15% scale) -> Goal: Visualize the de-escalating fee -> Viz: Line Chart (Chart.js) -> Interaction: Hover tooltips -> Justification: A line chart perfectly shows the *gradual* nature, which a table cannot.
        4. KPIs (Results): Report Info (+R$35M, 534% ROI, 55 Clientes, +R$30M Pipeline) -> Goal: High-impact stats -> Viz: HTML/Tailwind "Stat Cards" -> Justification: Easily scannable, high-impact numbers.
    -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
